Nutrient data for: CADBURY DAIRY MILK CHOCOLATE TABLET TRIO 300 GR, UNPREPARED, GTIN: 07622210989604
Food Group:  Branded Food Products Database

Ingredients: MILK**, sugar, cocoa butter, cocoa mass, skimmed MILK powder, whey powder (from MILK), MILK fat, vegetable fats (palm, shea), emulsifiers (SOYA lecithin, E442, E476, sunflower lecithin), flavourings, HAZELNUT paste. **The equivalent of 426ml of fresh liquid milk in every 227g of milk chocolate.CADBURY DAIRY MILK MILK CHOCOLATE: MILK SOLIDS 20% MINIMUM, ACTUAL 23%.COCOA SOLIDS 20% MINIMUM.CONTAINS VEGETABLE FATS IN ADDITION TO COCOA BUTTER.DARK MILK CHOCOLATE: MILK SOLIDS 14% MINIMUM.COCOA SOLIDS 45% MINIMUM.CONTAINS VEGETABLE FATS IN ADDITION TO COCOA BUTTER. MAY CONTAIN OTHER NUTS, WHEAT. Date available: 03/27/2018 Date last updated by company: 03/27/2018
